<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>New Form Submission</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981 0%, #059669 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5 0%, #7C3AED 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .submission-details {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #10B981;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>üìù New Form Submission</h1>
    <p>You have received a new submission!</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{ownerName}},</p>
    
    <p>Great news! Your form "<strong>{{formTitle}}</strong>" has received a new submission.</p>
    
    <div class="submission-details">
      <p><strong>Submission ID:</strong> {{submissionId}}</p>
      <p><strong>Submitted by:</strong> {{submittedBy}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{submissionDate}} at {{submissionTime}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{viewSubmissionUrl}}" class="button">View Full Submission</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>Keep up the great work with {{appName}}!</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This notification was sent because you own the form "{{formTitle}}".</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 